@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/spotify

### Import incremental normal (usa cursor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/import
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Import incremental limitando páginas (debug)
POST {{baseUrl}}/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxPages": 2
}

### Import resetando cursor (reimporta tudo que a API ainda retorna)
POST {{baseUrl}}/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resetCursor": true
}

### Reset + limite (debug controlado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resetCursor": true,
  "maxPages": 1
}

### Backfill de tracklist de álbuns (Spotify)
POST {{baseUrl}}/backfill-album-tracks?limit=50
